title: Turkish Airlines cargo jet crash kills 16 in Kyrgyzstan
text:
Turkish Airlines cargo jet crash kills 16 in Kyrgyzstan Agencies | Updated: 2017-01-16 11:14 
BISHKEK - A Turkish Airlines cargo jet crashed near Kyrgyzstan's Manas airport on Monday, killing at least 16 people, the Kyrgyz government said. 
Rescue workers have recovered the body of one pilot and 15 local people whose houses were in the Boeing 747 jet's crash area, the healthcare ministry said. Photo MOBILE Copyright 1995 - .
